		"description": "<p>At 17th level, you gain a token from the gods. While you are wearing the token, you are immune to fatigue and the blinded, deafened, and poisoned conditions. In addition, you can spend 1 exertion to use your @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.6akzshlvm3o5gggj]{Blessed Prowess} feature on any ability check, and you don&rsquo;t need to spend exertion to use @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.f4jzt1u42quvlwtx]{Sacred Boons}. Finally, when you roll initiative, you can roll your martial arts die and regain that much exertion.</p>\n<p>If your Eternal Favor token is destroyed, the gods bestow another token upon you after you complete an arduous task to prove you are still worthy.</p>",
